# Data

Examples use a labeled version of the `survival::colon` data set.

::: columns
::: {.column width="50%"}
::: {.cell hash='index_cache/revealjs/unnamed-chunk-2_7d3e0e5413be394ee5324ef5ce3c710e'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(ggsurvfit)
library(gtsummary)
library(tidyverse)

df_colon <- df_colon |> select(time, status, surg)
df_colon
```

